<module>
    <h>beag</h>
    <p><g>beag</g>
        <adj/>
        <en>small, little</en></p>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <section id="nouns-people">
            <h>people</h>
            <p>Examples with proper nouns – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri beag.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is small.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Bha torman an uillt a’ dèanamh ciùil ann an cluais Chaluim bhig.</gd>
                        <tr>The murmur of the burn was making music in little Malcolm’s ear.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 146</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with common nouns – <ul>
                    <li><g><a href="?gd=caileag">caileag</a> bheag</g>
                        <en>a little girl</en> – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Tha a’ chaileag beag.</gd>
                                <tr>The girl is small.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 15</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Chan eil a’ chaileag bheag anns an sgoil.</gd>
                                <tr>The little girl is not in the school.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td 14 [228]</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl></li>
                    <li><g><a href="?gd=gille">gille</a> beag</g>
                        <en>a little boy</en> – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Càit a bheil an gille beag an diugh?</gd>
                                <tr>Where is the little boy today?</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Có tha anns a’ chraoibh? Tha an gille beag.</gd>
                                <tr>Who is in the tree? The little boy is.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 40</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Nigh an gille beag a làmhan.</gd>
                                <tr>The little boy washed his hands.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>An do sheas an gille beag aig an uinneig? Sheas.</gd>
                                <tr>Did the little boy stand at the window? Yes, he did.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 54</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl></li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p> </p>
        </section>
